data.comment: Not the best run but had to submit for some points for league.

I wrote a whole essay explaining my feelings on what happened with this run, but I guess srcom wouldn't let me submit it, and I didn't even wanna have to go so deep with it, but I have to at least explain myself here, because otherwise, people will think I cheated, and if anybody in the romhack community knows me at all, you know I work too hard to need to cheat.  So, I'll be calmer and sum it up, since I sort of got it all out in the moment of drafting it up the first time.

The key points are as follows. I didn't realize that at some point between my last night's session and this one, that I accidentally had my audio capture on OBS muted, and did not think to check it beforehand.  I was going off on how much of a snake OBS was, but maybe I was just that stupid at the time, and maybe something suspicious like this had to happen in order for me to finally get a time I can be perfectly fine with submitting, despite me choking 16:3x on the last star, but nerves were bad anyway and I probably would've choked even worse on asta room, (like I did on a mid 16:4x pace a couple days prior), if I didn't choke then on said star, but I guess after how much stuff like this has happened over the course of the last 3-4 years, that's probably just who I was called to be, a choke artist, despite all my efforts to get better.

Also, my mouse was moving mid menuing in vanish cap, I still don't even fully know why I did that, and I have no reason to even do that, since I have no cheats and no enhancements added anywhere for this rom.  Maybe the nerves get me that much on a good run, that it just needs to happen, I don't know.  I wish I did, but I'm sorry if this invalidates my run.

Mod note: Please don't be hard on yourself
